1
00:00:00,690 --> 00:00:02,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you feel about nurse uniforms?</font>

2
00:00:02,570 --> 00:00:04,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean you want to see Lynn in one?</font>

3
00:00:03,100 --> 00:00:03,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Me?</font>

4
00:00:04,530 --> 00:00:05,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Huh?</font>

5
00:00:04,530 --> 00:00:07,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to see ya, kiddo.</font>

6
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:11,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have some great deals 
to share with you today, kiddo.</font>

7
00:00:13,100 --> 00:00:14,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There.</font>

8
00:00:14,080 --> 00:00:17,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have all these premium items
 at super low prices,</font>

9
00:00:17,830 --> 00:00:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but this offer is today only, kiddo.</font>

10
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:24,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You even brought weapons. 
They look like antiques, though.</font>

11
00:00:24,450 --> 00:00:26,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a pile of junk.</font>

12
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:28,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can tell you don't have 
an eye for quality, kiddo.</font>

13
00:00:28,870 --> 00:00:33,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Arne, anyway, kiddo? Arne? Arne?</font>

14
00:00:33,090 --> 00:00:34,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He can't hear you.</font>

15
00:00:34,470 --> 00:00:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kiddo?</font>

16
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:36,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zwei isn't here right now.</font>

17
00:00:36,870 --> 00:00:37,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kiddo!</font>

18
00:00:37,980 --> 00:00:40,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He said he was going out, 
but that was about three days ago.</font>

19
00:00:40,690 --> 00:00:41,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

20
00:00:42,800 --> 00:00:46,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where could Lord Arne have run off to?</font>

21
00:00:47,020 --> 00:00:49,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}PART 11: BIRDS OF A FEATHER FLOCK TOGETHER</font>

22
00:00:50,270 --> 00:00:54,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of our recent cases 
have something in common.</font>

23
00:00:54,070 --> 00:00:55,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that is?</font>

24
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:56,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Paintings.</font>

25
00:00:56,350 --> 00:00:57,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Paintings?</font>

26
00:00:57,650 --> 00:00:59,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">During the Medusa
 and leannán sídhe case,</font>

27
00:00:59,830 --> 00:01:01,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there was one in Medusa's house.</font>

28
00:01:03,820 --> 00:01:05,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">During the invisible man case,</font>

29
00:01:06,090 --> 00:01:08,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there was one in the family manor.</font>

30
00:01:08,960 --> 00:01:11,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">During the golem case,
the witch's restaurant had one.</font>

31
00:01:12,550 --> 00:01:18,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We saw some in the cat-sìth 
and mermaid cases, too.</font>

32
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:24,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words, I suspect 
that behind the scenes,</font>

33
00:01:24,520 --> 00:01:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all of these cases are connected 
by a single painter.</font>

34
00:01:29,370 --> 00:01:34,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That one's by a talented painter 
with a very promising future ahead.</i></font>

35
00:01:35,110 --> 00:01:40,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yet not even the art museum director knew
 the painter's whereabouts or identity.</font>

36
00:01:40,540 --> 00:01:42,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You never fail to impress, Lord Arne!</font>

37
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:46,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You went off alone 
to solve another mystery!</font>

38
00:01:46,720 --> 00:01:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My respect for you grows and grows!</font>

39
00:01:50,870 --> 00:01:52,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's pay this painter a visit.</font>

40
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

41
00:01:57,380 --> 00:01:59,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This must be it.</font>

42
00:01:59,260 --> 00:02:03,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lynn Reinweiß. Toss Nachzehrer 
over the gate so he can nose around.</font>

43
00:02:03,310 --> 00:02:04,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

44
00:02:04,310 --> 00:02:06,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't do that!</font>

45
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:12,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's right. It was an absolute nightmare 
washing the filth off from that air duct.</font>

46
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you remember 
what Amy always says?</font>

47
00:02:15,010 --> 00:02:18,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Giving a real dog a bath 
is easier than this."</font>

48
00:02:18,490 --> 00:02:22,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you quit worrying about how I look 
and spare a thought for my feelings?!</font>

49
00:02:23,700 --> 00:02:25,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen to me!</font>

50
00:02:45,850 --> 00:02:50,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}LOUIS HARTMANN'S FINAL CASE</font>

51
00:02:46,580 --> 00:02:48,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that Louis?</font>

52
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:02,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THE CASEBOOK OF ARNE</font>

53
00:04:22,950 --> 00:04:24,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Louis?</font>

54
00:04:24,330 --> 00:04:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's that?</font>

55
00:04:25,810 --> 00:04:28,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad I got to see you guys again.</font>

56
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:30,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impossible.</font>

57
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:34,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Louis Hartmann 
unmistakably lost his life.</font>

58
00:04:36,590 --> 00:04:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So why is he here?</font>

59
00:04:38,180 --> 00:04:39,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does this mean?</font>

60
00:04:39,990 --> 00:04:44,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't understand it either, 
but I woke up and was alive again.</font>

61
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:46,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You came back to life?</font>

62
00:04:46,300 --> 00:04:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't know what was going on,
 so I went to the police,</font>

63
00:04:50,970 --> 00:04:54,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but as soon as they saw me,
 they started yelling, "Zombie!"</font>

64
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:55,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and kicked up a huge fuss.</font>

65
00:04:56,030 --> 00:04:58,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I left Blumenstadt.</font>

66
00:04:58,580 --> 00:05:01,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But are you really Louis?</font>

67
00:05:01,790 --> 00:05:05,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I'm Louis Hartmann, 
the one and only.</font>

68
00:05:08,590 --> 00:05:13,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, since I've got you all here, why not
 come in and look at my paintings?</font>

69
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a painter now.
I'm kind of new to it, though.</font>

70
00:05:20,320 --> 00:05:21,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure. Let's take a look.</font>

71
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:29,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're in here.</font>

72
00:05:32,420 --> 00:05:34,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feel free to look around.</font>

73
00:05:43,990 --> 00:05:45,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

74
00:05:53,260 --> 00:05:55,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't look at them, Lynn Reinweiß.</font>

75
00:05:56,030 --> 00:06:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These paintings are designed to instill 
bloodlust and greed within the viewer.</font>

76
00:06:00,620 --> 00:06:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bloodlust and greed?</font>

77
00:06:09,440 --> 00:06:10,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lynn?</font>

78
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:25,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't this...</font>

79
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:33,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You painted the painting
 my father owned?</font>

80
00:06:34,220 --> 00:06:38,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, but I don't really keep track
 of who gets my paintings.</font>

81
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not Louis.</font>

82
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not Louis, are you?</font>

83
00:06:48,660 --> 00:06:50,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lynn?</font>

84
00:06:54,180 --> 00:06:57,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Hartmann Detective Agency 
is after that killer!</i></font>

85
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i></i>I'm<i> going to catch him!</i></font>

86
00:06:59,470 --> 00:07:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I must avenge my father's murder!</i></font>

87
00:07:02,300 --> 00:07:08,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Louis wanted to be a detective.
Not a painter, nor anything else.</font>

88
00:07:10,510 --> 00:07:16,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is your painting what caused 
my father to act the way he did?</font>

89
00:07:16,310 --> 00:07:19,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really don't know what you mean.</font>

90
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your painting...</font>

91
00:07:23,300 --> 00:07:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It made my father...</font>

92
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:29,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It made my kind, dear father...</font>

93
00:07:32,930 --> 00:07:37,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll never forgive you for what you did
 to my father and my home.</font>

94
00:07:38,650 --> 00:07:41,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long are you going 
to keep imitating Louis?</font>

95
00:07:41,980 --> 00:07:43,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reveal your true identity!</font>

96
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True identity?</font>

97
00:07:44,650 --> 00:07:45,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right <i>now</i>!</font>

98
00:07:51,670 --> 00:07:55,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shame. I'd hoped to stay 
like this a while longer.</font>

99
00:08:16,430 --> 00:08:18,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am known as Vlad.</font>

100
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:22,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vlad? Vlad the Third?</font>

101
00:08:23,590 --> 00:08:25,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vlad Țepeș?</font>

102
00:08:26,260 --> 00:08:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vlad the Impaler?</font>

103
00:08:28,050 --> 00:08:30,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? What a well-informed girl.</font>

104
00:08:31,230 --> 00:08:33,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've heard of him, Lynn?</font>

105
00:08:33,400 --> 00:08:36,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's one of the nine vampire kings,</font>

106
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:39,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">also known as Count Dracula.</font>

107
00:08:39,610 --> 00:08:42,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't been called by that name in ages.</font>

108
00:08:43,180 --> 00:08:46,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait a sec. Dracula? The vampire king?</font>

109
00:08:46,590 --> 00:08:48,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I remember now!</font>

110
00:08:48,130 --> 00:08:50,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, it's been a super long time!</font>

111
00:08:50,390 --> 00:08:53,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have no recollection
 of you whatsoever.</font>

112
00:08:53,630 --> 00:08:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. My heart is inside this guy right now.</font>

113
00:08:57,280 --> 00:08:59,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's me. Nachzehrer!</font>

114
00:09:00,370 --> 00:09:02,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nachzehrer?</font>

115
00:09:03,350 --> 00:09:07,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You <i>must</i> remember who I am! 
I'm one of the vampire kings, too!</font>

116
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:21,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, as you have now realized,</font>

117
00:09:21,840 --> 00:09:24,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it was all a vampire's fault.</font>

118
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:28,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A vampire's fault?</font>

119
00:09:28,920 --> 00:09:33,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came here to confront 
whoever had caused this mess,</font>

120
00:09:33,010 --> 00:09:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I never expected 
to find a vampire king.</font>

121
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:36,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is indeed a surprise.</font>

122
00:09:36,980 --> 00:09:40,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did not realize you were 
Neuntöte until just now.</font>

123
00:09:41,030 --> 00:09:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a coincidence that the individual 
who sensed the power in my paintings</font>

124
00:09:45,220 --> 00:09:48,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and tracked me down was,
 in fact, my counterpart.</font>

125
00:09:49,190 --> 00:09:51,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A vampire's fault?</font>

126
00:09:51,860 --> 00:09:54,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's a good girl. See that?</i></font>

127
00:09:54,850 --> 00:09:57,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There is a vampire standing 
right before your eyes.</i></font>

128
00:09:58,820 --> 00:10:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A wretched vampire.</i></font>

129
00:10:01,490 --> 00:10:04,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A wretched vampire.</font>

130
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:06,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You should kill him.</i></font>

131
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kill him.</font>

132
00:10:13,040 --> 00:10:14,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kill him.</i></font>

133
00:10:14,300 --> 00:10:15,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kill him.</font>

134
00:10:17,180 --> 00:10:18,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll kill him.</font>

135
00:10:18,550 --> 00:10:21,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll kill you, Arne Neuntöte!</font>

136
00:10:25,470 --> 00:10:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll kill you! I'll kill you! I'll kill you!</font>

137
00:10:27,680 --> 00:10:28,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with her?</font>

138
00:10:28,650 --> 00:10:30,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the paintings. They're too powerful.</font>

139
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:33,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll kill you. I'll kill you. 
I'll kill you. I'll kill you.</font>

140
00:10:34,980 --> 00:10:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Settle down, Lynn Reinweiß.</font>

141
00:10:37,910 --> 00:10:40,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was I just doing?</font>

142
00:10:40,030 --> 00:10:41,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How annoying.</font>

143
00:10:41,430 --> 00:10:43,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do not interrupt, my counterpart.</font>

144
00:10:44,380 --> 00:10:47,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I'm your "counterpart," 
why are you trying to make her kill me?</font>

145
00:10:47,650 --> 00:10:51,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way a young girl 
could kill you, is there?</font>

146
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:55,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vampires aren't the ones who get killed.</font>

147
00:10:57,460 --> 00:10:59,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They do the killing.</font>

148
00:11:02,050 --> 00:11:03,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lynn!</font>

149
00:11:09,230 --> 00:11:10,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne!</font>

150
00:11:11,430 --> 00:11:14,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, why would Neuntöte 
be protecting a human?</font>

151
00:11:14,990 --> 00:11:16,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Especially when he's my counterpart?</font>

152
00:11:17,170 --> 00:11:21,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you calling a "counterpart"? 
Your delusions are getting the best of you.</font>

153
00:11:22,250 --> 00:11:26,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? It seems you still have 
enough spirit to malign me.</font>

154
00:11:27,680 --> 00:11:30,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that will change very soon.</font>

155
00:11:48,390 --> 00:11:49,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne!</font>

156
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:55,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. It seems it was true that 
his heart was inside Neuntöte.</font>

157
00:11:55,440 --> 00:11:56,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne!</font>

158
00:11:56,140 --> 00:11:57,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Stop, Lynn.</font>

159
00:11:57,750 --> 00:11:58,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please let go of me!</font>

160
00:11:58,970 --> 00:12:01,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we try something now, we're done for.</font>

161
00:12:01,370 --> 00:12:02,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's retreat.</font>

162
00:12:05,280 --> 00:12:07,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne!</font>

163
00:12:14,390 --> 00:12:20,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I fail to see why my counterpart would
 risk his body to protect that human.</font>

164
00:12:20,800 --> 00:12:23,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Arne! I will come back to save you!</font>

165
00:12:24,260 --> 00:12:25,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Save him, huh?</font>

166
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The trivial ramblings of a human girl.</font>

167
00:12:29,380 --> 00:12:32,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You shouldn't underestimate
 Lynn Reinweiß.</i></font>

168
00:12:32,090 --> 00:12:35,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I can hear you, my young counterpart.</font>

169
00:12:36,220 --> 00:12:37,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very impressive.</font>

170
00:12:37,890 --> 00:12:43,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And yet, by now, you shouldn't 
be able to move an inch.</font>

171
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:46,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess we'll see.</i></font>

172
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can see you also hate to lose.</font>

173
00:12:51,270 --> 00:12:54,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps I have inherited 
Neuntöte's tenacity.</font>

174
00:12:56,160 --> 00:12:57,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How very interesting.</font>

175
00:13:02,770 --> 00:13:08,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Young human girl. If you wish 
to rescue Neuntöte, come to my castle.</font>

176
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:10,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Castle?</font>

177
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:13,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I look forward to your visit.</font>

178
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:19,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zisye! Amy! I need your help.</font>

179
00:13:19,490 --> 00:13:22,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to save Lord Arne!</font>

180
00:13:22,050 --> 00:13:25,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. I'll let Leah know, too.</font>

181
00:13:25,520 --> 00:13:30,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The werewolf community's in chaos right now,
 thanks to Count Dracula's paintings.</font>

182
00:13:33,090 --> 00:13:38,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, please tell Little Red that 
Amy and I are heading to the castle.</font>

183
00:13:38,630 --> 00:13:39,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Castle?</font>

184
00:13:39,770 --> 00:13:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dracula's castle, of course.</font>

185
00:13:41,890 --> 00:13:43,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dracula's castle?</font>

186
00:13:41,890 --> 00:13:43,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Dracula's castle?</font>

187
00:13:43,300 --> 00:13:46,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are two castles 
referred to as Dracula's castle.</font>

188
00:13:46,680 --> 00:13:51,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first one is Bran Castle, 
but Vlad only stayed there for a short time.</font>

189
00:13:51,820 --> 00:13:56,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I expect the other castle, 
Poenari Castle, is where he is right now.</font>

190
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:02,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A floor map of the castle? 
You're always so prepared, Lynn.</font>

191
00:14:02,360 --> 00:14:05,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dracula's castle is a key part 
of vampire history, after all.</font>

192
00:14:05,910 --> 00:14:09,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Poenari Castle, huh? 
Got it. I'll tell Leah.</font>

193
00:14:09,520 --> 00:14:10,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please do.</font>

194
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:12,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lynn.</font>

195
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:16,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just between us, 
I must be honest and tell you</font>

196
00:14:17,620 --> 00:14:22,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that I am unfortunately not confident
I will be able to protect you from Vlad.</font>

197
00:14:23,450 --> 00:14:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, Amy?</font>

198
00:14:25,250 --> 00:14:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As you can see, I am a delicate 
and darling young lady.</font>

199
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:33,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When it comes to fighting, 
I'm much weaker than Zwei or Little Red.</font>

200
00:14:33,640 --> 00:14:37,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Nachzehrer is nothing 
but a stuffed animal now.</font>

201
00:14:37,790 --> 00:14:42,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I think of the danger 
I might be putting you in, I can't...</font>

202
00:14:42,890 --> 00:14:43,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't...</font>

203
00:14:44,880 --> 00:14:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amy.</font>

204
00:14:46,640 --> 00:14:48,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think that will be a problem.</font>

205
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:48,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

206
00:14:48,950 --> 00:14:52,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because we will be facing off
 at Dracula's castle!</font>

207
00:14:55,980 --> 00:14:57,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see what you mean.</font>

208
00:15:08,830 --> 00:15:10,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't sleep?</font>

209
00:15:10,800 --> 00:15:13,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm too worried about Lord Arne.</font>

210
00:15:13,690 --> 00:15:16,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand, but you need sleep.</font>

211
00:15:16,300 --> 00:15:18,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are still human, Lynn.</font>

212
00:15:18,850 --> 00:15:19,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

213
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sweet dreams.</font>

214
00:15:32,830 --> 00:15:35,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Little Red Phantom Thief 
has marvelously arrived.</font>

215
00:15:35,880 --> 00:15:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And my appearance today 
is even more marvelous than usual.</font>

216
00:15:40,600 --> 00:15:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It seems Lady Lynn 
and the others aren't here yet.</font>

217
00:15:44,340 --> 00:15:46,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong, Leah?</font>

218
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:50,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe I smell blood. 
It's coming from the castle.</font>

219
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:55,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose I should go investigate
 the castle marvelously.</font>

220
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:24,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that...</font>

221
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:31,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leah!</font>

222
00:16:32,510 --> 00:16:36,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is nothing marvelous 
about a sneak attack.</font>

223
00:16:36,800 --> 00:16:42,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It appears I will have to show you 
what a truly marvelous fight looks like.</font>

224
00:16:42,510 --> 00:16:43,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leah!</font>

225
00:16:53,950 --> 00:16:56,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? They have arrived,</font>

226
00:16:56,990 --> 00:17:00,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">still unaware they'll be killed
 the moment we meet.</font>

227
00:17:03,110 --> 00:17:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You will regret making 
an enemy of Lynn Reinweiß.</i></font>

228
00:17:12,430 --> 00:17:14,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This looks like a good place for it.</font>

229
00:17:14,840 --> 00:17:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get started.</font>

230
00:17:15,870 --> 00:17:17,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please.</font>

231
00:17:42,300 --> 00:17:44,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like your plan is a success.</font>

232
00:17:45,040 --> 00:17:48,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vlad the Third is said to have 
taken more than 80,000 lives,</font>

233
00:17:48,690 --> 00:17:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the bodies are all buried here.</font>

234
00:17:51,410 --> 00:17:54,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This castle is the best.</font>

235
00:17:55,490 --> 00:18:01,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heave-ho. Heave-ho. 
Heave-ho. Heave-ho.</font>

236
00:18:01,590 --> 00:18:04,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why are we making them do this?</font>

237
00:18:04,030 --> 00:18:07,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, why not? 
Walking gets tedious sometimes.</font>

238
00:18:08,470 --> 00:18:12,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I knew it was going to be this easy, 
I would've brought tea and snacks.</font>

239
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:18,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here they come.</font>

240
00:18:18,020 --> 00:18:20,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enemies at 12 o'clock. 
We must breach their defenses.</font>

241
00:18:22,060 --> 00:18:23,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

242
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:29,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Forward.</font>

243
00:18:38,490 --> 00:18:40,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heave-ho!</font>

244
00:18:40,770 --> 00:18:42,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, good. That's the spirit.</font>

245
00:18:42,740 --> 00:18:48,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no reason to fear their weapons. 
After all, you're already dead.</font>

246
00:18:51,380 --> 00:18:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It appears the enemies 
aren't normal soldiers, either.</font>

247
00:18:55,120 --> 00:18:56,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

248
00:18:56,280 --> 00:19:00,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were probably once humans 
whose blood was drained by Vlad.</font>

249
00:19:01,150 --> 00:19:02,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lynn.</font>

250
00:19:02,350 --> 00:19:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zisye?</font>

251
00:19:03,120 --> 00:19:04,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leah is in trouble.</font>

252
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:06,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll show you where she is, so follow me.</font>

253
00:19:06,950 --> 00:19:08,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Little Red is in trouble?</font>

254
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:10,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go and help her, Lynn.</font>

255
00:19:10,250 --> 00:19:12,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me take care of things here.</font>

256
00:19:12,570 --> 00:19:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you three.</font>

257
00:19:14,910 --> 00:19:15,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

258
00:19:16,420 --> 00:19:19,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I order you to accompany Lynn.</font>

259
00:19:19,070 --> 00:19:22,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen. You must protect her at all costs.</font>

260
00:19:22,480 --> 00:19:24,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood!</font>

261
00:19:27,940 --> 00:19:29,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry, Lynn.</font>

262
00:19:29,520 --> 00:19:30,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

263
00:19:30,890 --> 00:19:32,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take me that way, and hurry!</font>

264
00:19:32,990 --> 00:19:35,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

265
00:19:36,110 --> 00:19:41,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When we get home, you can thank me 
by putting on that nurse uniform, okay?</font>

266
00:19:41,540 --> 00:19:46,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll wear anything you want! 
Just be careful, okay?!</font>

267
00:20:01,600 --> 00:20:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These zombies are so strong!</font>

268
00:20:03,890 --> 00:20:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We strong!</font>

269
00:20:11,450 --> 00:20:12,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Turn there.</font>

270
00:20:13,440 --> 00:20:14,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here?</font>

271
00:20:14,020 --> 00:20:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, that's the room.</font>

272
00:20:16,040 --> 00:20:17,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

273
00:20:21,490 --> 00:20:23,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Little Red!</font>

274
00:20:24,450 --> 00:20:28,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was unable to see who attacked her, 
so it must have been a vampire.</font>

275
00:20:28,800 --> 00:20:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A really strong one at that.</font>

276
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:31,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vlad.</font>

277
00:20:31,520 --> 00:20:34,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, probably. Be careful, Lynn.</font>

278
00:20:47,450 --> 00:20:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vlad's paintings again.</font>

279
00:20:50,700 --> 00:20:52,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Try not to look at them.</font>

280
00:20:52,690 --> 00:20:56,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll try, but we need to get out
 of this room quickly.</font>

281
00:20:59,920 --> 00:21:02,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's give them everything we've got.</font>

282
00:21:02,410 --> 00:21:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here we go.</font>

283
00:21:03,860 --> 00:21:05,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Evilly!</font>

284
00:21:06,180 --> 00:21:08,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bloody!</font>

285
00:21:08,950 --> 00:21:11,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fantastic!</font>

286
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:18,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Neuntöte!</font>

287
00:21:32,520 --> 00:21:36,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TRANSLATION: MICHAEL ARNOLD</font>

288
00:21:36,150 --> 00:21:40,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TIMING: HENRY LIN
EDITING: SMR</font>

289
00:21:40,240 --> 00:21:43,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}QUALITY CONTROL: ELISABETH CRIST
